---
title: Scales
---

Scales is one of the Children of the Forest in service to Last Greenseer. He/she does not speak the Common Tongue. His/her true name is too long for the human tongue according to Leaf. Scales is one of the Children of the Forest with nut-brown skin that is dappled like a deer's with paler spots, and large ears and large eyes slitted like a cat's eyes. 


